Pɩnaɣ hɔɔlʊʊ kɛna alɩwaatʊ taa alɩwaayʊʊ nakʊyʊ nɛ kɩkɛna fenasɩ naadozo tɛ nabʊlɛ. Pʊtɔbʊʊ se yee pakpaɣ fenasɩ naadozo nɛ pɔsɔzɩ naadozɔ ɖɔɖɔ kɔyɔ pɩlaba fenasɩ looɖo nɛ nzɩ payaɣ se pɩnaɣ hɔɔlʊʊ. Pɩnaɣ hɔɔlʊʊ kɛna alɩwaatʊ taa alɩwaayʊʊ nakʊyʊ nɛ fenasɩ looɖo kpɛndʊna nɛ pɩla pɩnaɣ hɔɔlʊʊ yaa fenasɩ looɖo. Pʊtɔɔbʊʊ se fenasɩ looɖo taa lɛ, kpɩtaŋ nɛɛlɛ wɛna.

Pʊtɔbʊʊ se pɛtɛyɩ fenasɩ looɖo hɛkʊ taa kɛ nabudozo taa kɔyɔ fenasɩ naalɛ wɛna nɛ yee pɩkɛ nabʊlɛ taa pɛyaa kɔyɔ panaɣ fenasɩ naadozo. Pɩnaɣ taa kacalaɣ fenasɩ naadozo kɔyɔ: kɔlaɣ fenaɣ, lɛlaɣ nɛ lakɩŋ fenaɣ. Pɩnaɣ taa fenasɩ naadozo taa naalɛ ñɩnzɩ kɔyɔ: ɖomaɣ, agoza nɛ mɩsɩkʊm. Pɩnaɣ taa fenasɩ naadozo taa naadozo ñɩnzɩ kɔyɔ: hasɩyaɖɛ fenaɣ, kɩyɛna ñɩŋga nɛ salaŋ. Piyele pɩnaɣ taa fenasɩ naadozo kpaagbaa ñɩnzɩ kɔyɔ: aloma, kamɩŋ nɛ saŋayɩŋ. Pʊtɔbʊʊ se, pɩnaɣ taa lɛ fenasɩ naadozo wɛ tɔm naanza taa. Pɩnaɣ taa fenasɩ looɖo wɛ tɔm nabʊlɛ ɖeke nɛ nzɩ yɔ: kɔlaɣ fenaɣ, lɛlaɣ fenaɣ lakɩŋ fenaɣ, ɖomaɣ, agoza nɛ mɩsɩkʊm fenaɣ. Pɩnaɣ taa fenasɩ looɖo gbaagbaa ñɩnzɩ kɔyɔ: hasɩyaɖɛ fenaɣ, kɩyɛna ñɩŋga, salaŋ, aloma, kamɩŋ nɛ saŋayɩŋ. 
Kabɩyɛ taa lɛ pɩnaɣ hɔɔlʊʊ kʊɖʊmʊʊwɛɛ ɛzɩ payaɣʊ se yolum nɛ lʊŋgɩyɛ yɔ.
